info.description:
MCCDAQ is an interface USB-DAQ running only on windows (XP pro,W2K,Me,W98)
- Connect MCCDAQ (USB-1208LS) on USB port
- Install driver (see CDROM for MCCDAQ)
- Install this python package mccdaq.
